        "section_mUTjEF": {
          "type": "section",
          "settings": {
            "section_id": "",
            "header": "",
            "text": "<p>Through the Site and Services, you can place orders for fishing products (“Products”) in a la carte purchases (“Standalone Purchases”) or through a subscription (“Subscription”). You are responsible for knowing the local laws and ordinances that govern fishing activities wherever you may be fishing. Mystery Tackle Box will not be liable for your use of any Product ordered through the Services that are not legal to use wherever you may be fishing. Please note, all prices listed on the site are in U.S. currency.</p>",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_url": "",
            "note": ""
          }
        },
        "section_bVanB9": {
          "type": "section",
          "settings": {
            "section_id": "",
            "header": "<strong>Standalone Purchases</strong>",
            "text": "<p>You may make Standalone Purchases by selecting Products and adding them to your cart and then completing the purchase transaction process, as directed on the Site. By making a purchase through the Site, you are authorizing Mystery Tackle Box to charge the payment method (e.g., credit card) chosen for the amount indicated on the purchase confirmation page. Returns for Standalone Purchases are subject to Mystery Tackle Box’s Return Policy located at <a href=\"/pages/returns\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Returns & Exchanges\">https://mysterytacklebox.com/pages/returns</a>. The Return Policy is subject to change in our sole discretion without notice. Once you have made a Standalone Purchase, you may cancel your order so long as your order has not yet shipped. If you wish to cancel any Standalone Purchase, please contact Customer Service at <a href=\"mailto:support@mysterytacklebox.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"mailto:support@mysterytacklebox.com\">support@mysterytacklebox.com</a>. You must include your order number in your cancellation request.</p>",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_url": "",
            "note": ""
          }
        },
        "section_iVYmN4": {
          "type": "section",
          "settings": {
            "section_id": "",
            "header": "<strong>Subscriptions</strong>",
            "text": "<p>By registering an Account and enrolling in a Subscription (“Enrollment”), you will choose which of our periodic shipments you wish to receive, and also provide other information that will assist us in fulfilling your orders and your expectations. We will use such information to fulfill your periodic orders and we may use such information in order to present you with opportunities for additional products that we feel may be of interest to you. You will also register a payment method (e.g., a credit card) and such registration of your payment method constitutes your authorization to charge such amounts to that payment method and otherwise constitutes your promise to pay for items purchased from the Site.</p><p>Upon Enrollment, you will choose which one or more of our Product plans you wish to order. We will send shipments to you at the frequency and value that you choose. You acknowledge and agree that it is impossible for the value of our shipments to exactly equal the approximate value you have chosen, and your order from Mystery Tackle Box signifies your acknowledgment that the value of each shipment will be within one U.S. Dollar of the value that you have chosen. You may change the desired approximate value of your periodic shipment, or cancel your Subscription at any time. Any change or cancellation of Subscription will be effective immediately as to all Products not yet billed to your account as of the date and time of the change or cancellation. Products already billed but not sent as of the date and time of the change or cancellation will be sent as previously scheduled and cannot be refunded. You may change or cancel your Subscription by accessing your Account through the Site or by contacting Customer Service at <a href=\"mailto:support@mysterytacklebox.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"mailto:support@mysterytacklebox.com\">support@mysterytacklebox.com</a>.</p><p>Your use of the Site is your acknowledgement that you have enrolled to receive fishing-related products that are unknown to you at the time of ordering and receipt by you. Mystery Tackle Box offers no refunds or credits for returned Subscription Products except in our sole discretion. If you did not receive your Subscription shipment during any month, you must contact us within 30 days of that month's shipment date in order to receive a replacement.</p>",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_url": "",
            "note": ""
          }
        },
