        },
        "section_RRLttH": {
          "type": "section",
          "settings": {
            "section_id": "",
            "header": "<strong>Product Orders and Sales</strong>",
            "text": "<p>By placing an order using the Site and Services, a customer makes a binding offer for a contract of sale. We will send an order confirmation email to the customer. The order confirmation is not an acceptance of the order, but only an acknowledgment that the order was received. The offer is accepted when we confirm in a second email to the customer that we have either begun to process or shipped the order. We do not guarantee the continued availability of any Product found on the Site or Services. We reserve the right, without prior notice, to limit the order quantity on any Product and/or to refuse service to any customer. We also may require verification of information prior to the acceptance and/or shipment of any Product order.</p>",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_url": "",
            "note": ""
          }
        },
        "section_EMc8Gq": {
          "type": "section",
          "settings": {
            "section_id": "",
            "header": "<strong>Delivery, Shipment and Title</strong>",
            "text": "<p>We will make delivery of accepted Product orders in accordance with our Shipping Policy located at <a href=\"/pages/shipping\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Shipping Information\">https://mysterytacklebox.com/pages/shipping</a>. </p>",
