        "section_gtCJ4j": {
          "type": "section",
          "settings": {
            "section_id": "",
            "header": "<strong>Payments</strong>",
            "text": "<p>Customers may choose to pay by credit card or PayPal. We reserve the right to limit the method of payment chosen by the customer depending on order value, shipment destination, or other criteria. In addition, we may offer one-time promotional codes from time to time. One-time promotional codes may only be used once per household and we reserve the right to cancel orders made by customers abusing this policy. Additional terms may apply when you submit the promotional code on the Site.</p>",
